ğŸ§ . The terraform fmt command is used to format your Terraform configuration files 
  terraform fmt is used to automatically format Terraform configuration files (.tf files) into a standard, readable style.

terraform fmt -check       # Check formatting without modifying files
terraform fmt -diff        # Show differences before formatting

