ğŸ§ . What is Terraform?
  Terraform is an open-source infrastructure as code (IaC) tool developed by HashiCorp that allows users to define and provision data center infrastructure using a high-level
configuration language called HCL (HashiCorp Configuration Language) or JSON.
    Example:
provider "aws" {
region = "us-west-2"
}
resource "aws_instance" "example" {
ami = "ami-0c55b159cbfafe1f0"
instance_type = "t2.micro"
}

